OL,3,CFare dodgers face more fines on
OL,4,CTransport for Wales trains
OL,6,FFrom today (Monday, 9th September)
OL,7,Fpassengers who board trains without a
OL,8,Fticket face being fined on more lines.
OL,10,FThe penalty fare zone between Severn
OL,11,FTunnel Junction and Carmarthen is
OL,12,Fbeing extended to most of south Wales,
OL,13,Fincluding the Treherbert, Aberdare,
OL,14,FMerthyr, Coryton, Penarth, Rhymney,
OL,15,FBarry, Bridgend and the Ebbw Vale
OL,16,Flines.
OL,18,FFare dodgers face a fine of double the
OL,19,Fticket fare or #20, whichever is
OL,20,Fgreater.
